OL,3,CBristol independent shops to get #2k
OL,4,Cgrant to combat shoplifting 'epidemic'
OL,6,FIndependent shops in Bristol can now
OL,7,Fapply for a grant of up to #2,000 to
OL,8,Fhelp them tackle the shoplifting
OL,9,F'epidemic'.
OL,11,FShoplifting rates have shot up in the
OL,12,FWest of England by 41% over the past
OL,13,Fyear, with Bristol hit particularly
OL,14,Fhard by thieves.
OL,16,FOne shopkeeper in South Bristol said
OL,17,Fthieves regularly steal from his
OL,18,Fconvenience store, while the police
OL,19,Foften appear reluctant to investigate
OL,20,Fany reported crimes.
